{"tid":2203955,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國批評世貿所做事情完全不足　中國指世貿客觀公正","createTime":"2020-09-15T16:45:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T00:17:49.000Z","uid":125193,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"826f61611ac445ab45263be9754fb049e69de18d","tid":2203955,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T16:45:03.000Z","msg":"世界貿易組織裁定，美國在前年對中國加徵的關稅，不符合全球貿易規則。<br />\n<br />\n世貿組織一個3人小組裁定，華盛頓方面未能充分證明，引用301條款針對中國進行調查後徵收的關稅是「暫時合理」，建議美國採取貿易措施時要一致。<br />\n<br />\n美國回應裁決時批評，在促使中國承擔責任方面，世貿組織做的事情「完全不足夠」。<br />\n<br />\n美國貿易代表萊特希澤說，必須容許美國從不公平貿易操作當中，捍衛自身利益，又說總統特朗普政府不會容許中國利用世貿組織，佔美國工人、企業、牧場及農民的便宜。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1549808-20200916.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1549808-20200916.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIud3lGhCGuGi3hvupoSMmYHA%3D&h=514cedde\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1549808-20200916.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a978f25d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1549808-20200916.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"001aa3349e36e67d3e05e3f7f8d5bc05611719ab","tid":2203955,"uid":125193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T16:45:55.000Z","msg":"一唱一和<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29ba91859c6ca87fcb5e06d05208bc1bf6ba6e70","tid":2203955,"uid":2054,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T16:48:06.000Z","msg":"美國一星期內退出世貿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94ed1e93f2993ecde721a973c45b51b49d9196bc","tid":220